data.meta_description: CPL, US ARMY WORLD WAR II === The Courier-Journal (Louisville. KY) 18 Feb 1949  WARDER, Corporal Joseph H. Jr., aviation engineer, killed in action in 1945 on Luzon Island.  Survivors, wife, Mrs Rachel S. Warder; son, Hiram W Warder; mother, Mrs. Estelle Warder, all of Vincennes. Ind.; 2 brothers. Hiram W. Warder....
